<SiteLayout site="siliconbased" title="The 3 Minute Timer: The Micro-Habit That Prevents Developer Burnout" description="A 3 minute timer might seem too short to achieve anything. Yet, the world's most productive engineers use exactly this duration to bypass mental roadblocks..." canonical="https://siliconbased.dev/3-minute-timer" schema={schema}>
